<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="K" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Kernel" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Kernel,</orth> 1) the edible substance of a nut: <bibl n="shak. shr 2.257" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. II, 257</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.5.47" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 5, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 2.1.112" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. II, 1, 112</bibl>.
<lb />2) the seed of pulpy fruits: <bibl n="shak. tmp 2.1.92" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. II, 1, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 2.3.276" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 3, 276</bibl>.
<lb />3) Used to denote any thing diminutive: <cit><quote>how like I then was to this k.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.159" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 159</bibl></cit>.
